window.bookSummaryJSON = "<b><p>From <i>New York Times</i> best-selling author Katie MacAlister comes the first Dark Ones novella. </p></b> <p><b></b>Battling a demon lord is all in a day's work for the Dark One named Sebastian. But now he must take on a horde of unhappy zombies and an obnoxious teen vampire if he wants to win the hand of the one woman who can make him whole. </p> <p>Ysabelle is a woman with a past, and not a whole lot of future if a certain demon lord has his way. With zombies, demons, and a little thing like death standing in her way, will she find happiness in the man who's seen more darkness than she can imagine? </p> <p><b>Note:</b> this novella was published in 2006 and again in 2010 in the Just One Sip and My Zombie Valentine anthologies, respectively. Listeners should be aware that this is a republishing of a previously published novella. </p>"; 
